{
  "title": "Vibes, Veo 3, Ray3, Kling 2.5 : le point complet",
  "content": "<p data-start=\"40\" data-end=\"363\">En septembre, l&rsquo;IA vid&eacute;o a clairement chang&eacute; d&rsquo;&eacute;chelle :&nbsp;<strong data-start=\"97\" data-end=\"141\">Meta ouvre un feed 100 % vid&eacute;os g&eacute;n&eacute;r&eacute;es</strong>, <strong data-start=\"143\" data-end=\"185\">Google pousse Veo 3 dans Google Photos</strong>, <strong data-start=\"187\" data-end=\"227\">Luma lance Ray3 (raisonnement + HDR)</strong> et <strong data-start=\"231\" data-end=\"270\">Kuaishou upgrade Kling en 2.5 Turbo</strong>. Voici l&rsquo;essentiel, les impacts concrets pour vos contenus, et quoi faire d&egrave;s cette semaine.</p>\n<hr data-start=\"365\" data-end=\"368\">\n<h2 data-start=\"370\" data-end=\"444\">1) Plateformes : Meta lance <strong data-start=\"401\" data-end=\"410\">Vibes</strong>, un feed de vid&eacute;os 100 % g&eacute;n&eacute;r&eacute;es</h2>\n<p data-start=\"445\" data-end=\"865\">Meta a d&eacute;voil&eacute; <strong data-start=\"460\" data-end=\"469\">Vibes</strong> (26&ndash;27 sept.), un nouveau flux dans l&rsquo;app Meta AI et sur meta.ai, o&ugrave; tout est produit par des mod&egrave;les de g&eacute;n&eacute;ration vid&eacute;o. Les cr&eacute;ateurs peuvent partir de z&eacute;ro, remixer des clips du feed, ajouter visuels et musique, puis publier sur Vibes, <strong data-start=\"710\" data-end=\"719\">Reels</strong> ou <strong data-start=\"723\" data-end=\"734\">Stories</strong>. L&rsquo;objectif : industrialiser la cr&eacute;ativit&eacute; et&hellip; tester la mon&eacute;tisation d&rsquo;outils IA chez Meta. <span class=\"\" data-state=\"closed\"><span class=\"ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]\" data-testid=\"webpage-citation-pill\"><a class=\"flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]!\" href=\"https://www.reuters.com/business/meta-unveils-new-ai-video-feed-vibes-2025-09-25/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span class=\"relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center\"><span class=\"flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between overflow-hidden\"><span class=\"max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center\">Reuters</span></span></span></a></span></span></p>\n<p data-start=\"867\" data-end=\"1135\">C&ocirc;t&eacute; r&eacute;ception, la presse souligne &agrave; la fois le c&ocirc;t&eacute; fun (clips surr&eacute;alistes, &ldquo;kittens bakers&rdquo;, etc.) et le d&eacute;bat sur l&rsquo;&ldquo;<strong data-start=\"988\" data-end=\"999\">AI slop</strong>&rdquo; (contenus IA massifs de qualit&eacute; variable) ; Vibes est disponible dans plus de 40 pays (hors UK). <span class=\"\" data-state=\"closed\"><span class=\"ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]\" data-testid=\"webpage-citation-pill\"><a class=\"flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]!\" href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2025/sep/26/cute-fluffy-characters-and-egyptian-selfies-meta-launches-ai-feed-vibes\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span class=\"relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center\"><span class=\"flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between overflow-hidden\"><span class=\"max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center\">The Guardian</span></span></span></a></span></span></p>\n<p data-start=\"1137\" data-end=\"1185\"><strong data-start=\"1137\" data-end=\"1183\">Ce que &ccedil;a change pour vous (cr&eacute;ateurs/PME)</strong></p>\n<ul data-start=\"1186\" data-end=\"1451\">\n<li data-start=\"1186\" data-end=\"1331\">\n<p data-start=\"1188\" data-end=\"1331\">Reach potentiel via un <strong data-start=\"1211\" data-end=\"1246\">nouveau carrefour de d&eacute;couverte</strong> ; recyclez vos prompts/actifs pour des versions &laquo; verticales &raquo; pr&ecirc;tes &agrave; storyfier.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"1332\" data-end=\"1451\">\n<p data-start=\"1334\" data-end=\"1451\">Testez des <strong data-start=\"1345\" data-end=\"1363\">formats UGC IA</strong> (15&ndash;30 s) pour teaser produits ou features, puis faites l&rsquo;A/B test sur Reels &lt;-&gt; Vibes.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-start=\"1453\" data-end=\"1456\">\n<h2 data-start=\"1458\" data-end=\"1541\">2) Grand public : <strong data-start=\"1479\" data-end=\"1488\">Veo 3</strong> arrive dans <strong data-start=\"1501\" data-end=\"1518\">Google Photos</strong> (US), image-vers-vid&eacute;o</h2>\n<p data-start=\"1542\" data-end=\"1936\">Depuis le <strong data-start=\"1552\" data-end=\"1563\">4 sept.</strong>, <strong data-start=\"1565\" data-end=\"1574\">Veo 3</strong> s&rsquo;int&egrave;gre &agrave; Google Photos (onglet <em data-start=\"1609\" data-end=\"1617\">Create</em>). On s&eacute;lectionne une image &rarr; Google g&eacute;n&egrave;re un <strong data-start=\"1664\" data-end=\"1697\">clip court (&asymp;4 s, sans audio)</strong>, avec filigranes visibles/invisibles. Les abonn&eacute;s <strong data-start=\"1748\" data-end=\"1764\">AI Pro/Ultra</strong> ont plus de g&eacute;n&eacute;rations. C&rsquo;est US-only au lancement. Message : l&rsquo;IA vid&eacute;o sort des apps &ldquo;pro&rdquo; et entre dans l&rsquo;album de tout le monde. <span class=\"\" data-state=\"closed\"><span class=\"ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]\" data-testid=\"webpage-citation-pill\"><a class=\"flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]!\" href=\"https://techcrunch.com/2025/09/04/google-photos-adds-ai-video-generation-with-veo-3/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span class=\"relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center\"><span class=\"flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between overflow-hidden\"><span class=\"max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center\">TechCrunch</span></span></span></a></span></span></p>\n<p data-start=\"1938\" data-end=\"2186\"><strong data-start=\"1938\" data-end=\"1953\">Implication</strong> : attendez-vous &agrave; une <strong data-start=\"1976\" data-end=\"2020\">explosion d&rsquo;animations &ldquo;memory-to-video&rdquo;</strong> (avant/apr&egrave;s, portraits, objets). Si vous ciblez le march&eacute; US, pr&eacute;parez des <strong data-start=\"2097\" data-end=\"2118\">presets de styles</strong> (ex. &ldquo;pack ambiance marque&rdquo;) &agrave; appliquer depuis des photos clients.</p>\n<hr data-start=\"2188\" data-end=\"2191\">\n<h2 data-start=\"2193\" data-end=\"2269\">3) Course aux mod&egrave;les : <strong data-start=\"2220\" data-end=\"2228\">Ray3</strong> (Luma) et <strong data-start=\"2239\" data-end=\"2258\">Kling 2.5 Turbo</strong> (Kuaishou)</h2>\n<ul data-start=\"2271\" data-end=\"2974\">\n<li data-start=\"2271\" data-end=\"2673\">\n<p data-start=\"2273\" data-end=\"2673\"><strong data-start=\"2273\" data-end=\"2286\">Luma Ray3</strong> (18&ndash;23 sept.) : Luma annonce un <strong data-start=\"2319\" data-end=\"2346\">&ldquo;reasoning video model&rdquo;</strong> et du <strong data-start=\"2353\" data-end=\"2366\">HDR natif</strong> (10/12/16-bit, ACES EXR), plus un <strong data-start=\"2401\" data-end=\"2415\">Draft Mode</strong> pour it&eacute;rer vite. <strong data-start=\"2434\" data-end=\"2451\">Adobe Firefly</strong> devient premier partenaire d&rsquo;int&eacute;gration : g&eacute;n&eacute;ration Ray3 directement dans Firefly, avec <em data-start=\"2542\" data-end=\"2563\">Content Credentials</em> c&ocirc;t&eacute; Adobe. Signal fort : rapprochement IA vid&eacute;o &harr; cha&icirc;ne de prod cr&eacute;a. <span class=\"\" data-state=\"closed\"><span class=\"ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]\" data-testid=\"webpage-citation-pill\"><a class=\"flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]!\" href=\"https://petapixel.com/2025/09/23/adobe-adds-luma-ais-ray3-ai-video-generator-to-firefly/?utm_source=chatgpt.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span class=\"relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center\"><span class=\"flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center\">PetaPixel</span><span class=\"-me-1 flex h-full items-center rounded-full px-1 text-[#8F8F8F]\">+1</span></span></span></a></span></span></p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"2675\" data-end=\"2974\">\n<p data-start=\"2677\" data-end=\"2974\"><strong data-start=\"2677\" data-end=\"2696\">Kling 2.5 Turbo</strong> (23&ndash;26 sept.) : upgrade ax&eacute; <strong data-start=\"2725\" data-end=\"2755\">mouvements plus dynamiques</strong>, meilleure <strong data-start=\"2767\" data-end=\"2790\">adh&eacute;rence au prompt</strong> et <strong data-start=\"2794\" data-end=\"2823\">baisse de ~30 % des co&ucirc;ts</strong> vs 2.1 (cr&eacute;dits/5 s en 1080p). Kling reste l&rsquo;un des champions des <strong data-start=\"2890\" data-end=\"2913\">dur&eacute;es plus longues</strong> et de la <strong data-start=\"2923\" data-end=\"2935\">fluidit&eacute;</strong>. <span class=\"\" data-state=\"closed\"><span class=\"ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]\" data-testid=\"webpage-citation-pill\"><a class=\"flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]!\" href=\"https://www.marketscreener.com/news/kuaishou-technology-inc-launches-2-5-turbo-video-model-ce7d58d3d081f021?utm_source=chatgpt.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span class=\"relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center\"><span class=\"flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center\">MarketScreener</span><span class=\"-me-1 flex h-full items-center rounded-full px-1 text-[#8F8F8F]\">+1</span></span></span></a></span></span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-start=\"2976\" data-end=\"3017\"><strong data-start=\"2976\" data-end=\"3015\">Pour un tournage &ldquo;z&eacute;ro cam&rdquo; en 2025</strong></p>\n<ul data-start=\"3018\" data-end=\"3293\">\n<li data-start=\"3018\" data-end=\"3122\">\n<p data-start=\"3020\" data-end=\"3122\"><strong data-start=\"3020\" data-end=\"3060\">Cin&eacute;matique courte (annonce produit)</strong> : Ray3 (pour coh&eacute;rence, HDR et passage Firefly &rarr; Premiere).</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"3123\" data-end=\"3217\">\n<p data-start=\"3125\" data-end=\"3217\"><strong data-start=\"3125\" data-end=\"3158\">Clips plus longs / prix serr&eacute;</strong> : Kling 2.5 Turbo (dur&eacute;es &eacute;tendues, co&ucirc;t/it&eacute;ration bas).</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"3218\" data-end=\"3293\">\n<p data-start=\"3220\" data-end=\"3293\"><strong data-start=\"3220\" data-end=\"3244\">Story &ldquo;grand public&rdquo;</strong> : Veo 3 (pour photos&rarr;vid&eacute;os, &eacute;cosyst&egrave;me Google).</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-start=\"3295\" data-end=\"3298\">\n<h2 data-start=\"3300\" data-end=\"3360\">4) France/UE : <strong data-start=\"3318\" data-end=\"3326\">Sora</strong> est bien dispo (depuis f&eacute;v. 2025)</h2>\n<p data-start=\"3361\" data-end=\"3666\">Pour rappel, <strong data-start=\"3374\" data-end=\"3389\">OpenAI Sora</strong> est accessible en <strong data-start=\"3408\" data-end=\"3417\">UE/UK</strong> depuis fin f&eacute;vrier (Plus/Pro). Sp&eacute;cifications grand public (&agrave; ce jour) : jusqu&rsquo;&agrave; <strong data-start=\"3499\" data-end=\"3516\">20 s en 1080p</strong>, multiples formats, remix/extend. Pour un public fran&ccedil;ais, c&rsquo;est l&rsquo;option la plus &laquo; cl&eacute;-en-main &raquo; c&ocirc;t&eacute; ChatGPT. <span class=\"\" data-state=\"closed\"><span class=\"ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]\" data-testid=\"webpage-citation-pill\"><a class=\"flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]!\" href=\"https://techcrunch.com/2025/02/27/openais-sora-is-now-available-in-the-eu-uk/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span class=\"relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center\"><span class=\"flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between overflow-hidden\"><span class=\"max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center\">TechCrunch</span></span></span></a></span></span></p>\n<hr data-start=\"3668\" data-end=\"3671\">\n<h2 data-start=\"3673\" data-end=\"3752\">5) Distribution : <strong data-start=\"3694\" data-end=\"3704\">Envato</strong> l&egrave;ve (temporairement) les limites de g&eacute;n&eacute;ration</h2>\n<p data-start=\"3753\" data-end=\"4031\">Tendance &ldquo;d&eacute;blocage&rdquo; : Envato annonce <strong data-start=\"3791\" data-end=\"3817\">g&eacute;n&eacute;rations illimit&eacute;es</strong> (fair-use) tout septembre sur son outil, pilotant <strong data-start=\"3868\" data-end=\"3902\">Kling, Veo 3, Seedance, Hailuo</strong> sous le capot. Int&eacute;r&ecirc;t : <strong data-start=\"3928\" data-end=\"3943\">tester vite</strong> plusieurs mod&egrave;les sans jongler entre abonnements. <span class=\"\" data-state=\"closed\"><span class=\"ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]\" data-testid=\"webpage-citation-pill\"><a class=\"flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]!\" href=\"https://www.techradar.com/ai-platforms-assistants/want-to-try-ai-video-creation-envatos-removing-usage-limits-on-veo-3-and-kling-this-september?utm_source=chatgpt.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span class=\"relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center\"><span class=\"flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between overflow-hidden\"><span class=\"max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center\">TechRadar</span></span></span></a></span></span></p>\n<hr data-start=\"4033\" data-end=\"4036\">\n<h2 data-start=\"4038\" data-end=\"4089\">Impacts &amp; mini-reco (actionnables cette semaine)</h2>\n<p data-start=\"4091\" data-end=\"4126\"><strong data-start=\"4091\" data-end=\"4126\">Stack rapide selon votre profil</strong></p>\n<ul data-start=\"4127\" data-end=\"4560\">\n<li data-start=\"4127\" data-end=\"4267\">\n<p data-start=\"4129\" data-end=\"4267\"><strong data-start=\"4129\" data-end=\"4146\">D&eacute;butant/ind&eacute;</strong> : commencez par <strong data-start=\"4163\" data-end=\"4188\">Veo 3 (Google Photos)</strong> pour animer 10 visuels produits &rarr; montez un <strong data-start=\"4233\" data-end=\"4246\">reel MOFU</strong> (4&ndash;8 clips &times; 4 s).</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"4268\" data-end=\"4417\">\n<p data-start=\"4270\" data-end=\"4417\"><strong data-start=\"4270\" data-end=\"4288\">PME e-commerce</strong> : <strong data-start=\"4291\" data-end=\"4304\">Sora/Ray3</strong> pour 2&ndash;3 hooks 15&ndash;20 s (HDR si YouTube/CTV), avec <strong data-start=\"4355\" data-end=\"4370\">shoot mixte</strong> : 70 % IA, 30 % rushs r&eacute;els (mains/texture).</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"4418\" data-end=\"4560\">\n<p data-start=\"4420\" data-end=\"4560\"><strong data-start=\"4420\" data-end=\"4436\">Studio/brand</strong> : <strong data-start=\"4439\" data-end=\"4457\">Ray3 &rarr; Firefly</strong> (HDR + Content Credentials) pour pipeline color-managed, ou <strong data-start=\"4518\" data-end=\"4527\">Kling</strong> pour <strong data-start=\"4533\" data-end=\"4548\">it&eacute;rer long</strong> &agrave; bas co&ucirc;t.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-start=\"4562\" data-end=\"4661\"><strong data-start=\"4562\" data-end=\"4592\">Exemple terrain (PME d&eacute;co)</strong><br data-start=\"4592\" data-end=\"4595\">Brief : &ldquo;table basse en noyer, style japandi, lumi&egrave;re du matin&rdquo;.</p>\n<ul data-start=\"4662\" data-end=\"4942\">\n<li data-start=\"4662\" data-end=\"4763\">\n<p data-start=\"4664\" data-end=\"4763\"><strong data-start=\"4664\" data-end=\"4672\">Ray3</strong> : moodboard &rarr; plan 6 s &ldquo;d&eacute;ballage + pose&rdquo;, export EXR 16-bit &rarr; &eacute;talonnage doux, titrage.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"4764\" data-end=\"4852\">\n<p data-start=\"4766\" data-end=\"4852\"><strong data-start=\"4766\" data-end=\"4775\">Kling</strong> : version 18&ndash;24 s avec <strong data-start=\"4799\" data-end=\"4825\">travelling + cut sc&egrave;ne</strong> (main qui pose un vase).</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"4853\" data-end=\"4942\">\n<p data-start=\"4855\" data-end=\"4942\"><strong data-start=\"4855\" data-end=\"4867\">A/B test</strong> : publiez 2 montages (HDR vs standard) et suivez temps de r&eacute;tention &gt; 5 s.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-start=\"4944\" data-end=\"4971\"><strong data-start=\"4944\" data-end=\"4971\">Deux erreurs fr&eacute;quentes</strong></p>\n<ol data-start=\"4972\" data-end=\"5210\">\n<li data-start=\"4972\" data-end=\"5072\">\n<p data-start=\"4975\" data-end=\"5072\"><strong data-start=\"4975\" data-end=\"5010\">Sous-&eacute;crire les droits/licences</strong> (fichiers sans <em data-start=\"5026\" data-end=\"5047\">Content Credentials</em>, musiques non-libres).</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"5073\" data-end=\"5210\">\n<p data-start=\"5076\" data-end=\"5210\"><strong data-start=\"5076\" data-end=\"5103\">Prompt trop &ldquo;g&eacute;n&eacute;rique&rdquo;</strong> &rarr; outputs lisses. Ajoutez <strong data-start=\"5130\" data-end=\"5154\">r&eacute;f&eacute;rences visuelles</strong> (texture bois, angle 35 mm, &ldquo;dawn soft shadows&rdquo;, etc.).</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p data-start=\"5212\" data-end=\"5228\"><strong data-start=\"5212\" data-end=\"5228\">3 quick wins</strong></p>\n<ul data-start=\"5229\" data-end=\"5513\">\n<li data-start=\"5229\" data-end=\"5318\">\n<p data-start=\"5231\" data-end=\"5318\"><strong data-start=\"5231\" data-end=\"5266\">R&eacute;utilisez vos shoots existants</strong> : <strong data-start=\"5269\" data-end=\"5286\">image-&rarr;-vid&eacute;o</strong> (Veo 3) multiplie vos assets.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"5319\" data-end=\"5425\">\n<p data-start=\"5321\" data-end=\"5425\"><strong data-start=\"5321\" data-end=\"5349\">Verrouillez la coh&eacute;rence</strong> : <strong data-start=\"5352\" data-end=\"5387\">r&eacute;f&eacute;rence de personnage/produit</strong> (Kling/Ray3) pour styles constants.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"5426\" data-end=\"5513\">\n<p data-start=\"5428\" data-end=\"5513\"><strong data-start=\"5428\" data-end=\"5439\">Marquez</strong> vos contenus (C2PA/Content Credentials) et conservez les logs de prompts.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-start=\"5515\" data-end=\"5518\">\n<h2 data-start=\"5520\" data-end=\"5544\">Vigilance &ldquo;deepfakes&rdquo;</h2>\n<p data-start=\"5545\" data-end=\"5803\">La circulation de vid&eacute;os IA trompeuses rappelle l&rsquo;importance des <strong data-start=\"5610\" data-end=\"5624\">filigranes</strong> et v&eacute;rifications &eacute;ditoriales avant diffusion sociale/paid. Gardez un process de <strong data-start=\"5705\" data-end=\"5722\">revue interne</strong> (2 paires d&rsquo;yeux + check des m&eacute;tadonn&eacute;es). <span class=\"\" data-state=\"closed\"><span class=\"ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]\" data-testid=\"webpage-citation-pill\"><a class=\"flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-o